Package: shiny.ollama
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Shiny Interface for Ollama
Description: Provides an R Shiny interface to interact with large language models (LLMs) locally using Ollama. 
    This package enables seamless integration of conversational AI capabilities into Shiny applications, 
    offering an efficient and user-friendly interface for local LLM usage.
